{
  "stem": "4272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a foreman at this-- at this factory where we worked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he took her out, but then his wife would not allow him to keep her overnight there because she was afraid that if the Germans would find out, they would kill the whole family.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which in a way, I cannot blame her for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But anyhow, he came back once to the-- I did not go back to camp after-- it's-- I-- I can't, you know, to make you understand it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he came and he killed, let's say, 50 people, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and that was the time to escape because they put you on the list of the killed and nobody had to be killed for you when you escaped.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that it was, Jews were watching each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when my sister was sick, there were people that came over to me and he said, look, you give your life for your sister.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm not willing to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then they came, they said, now it's the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Today or never.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because we'll put you on the list of the dead and that's it, and nobody will pay for it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the day when I-- I had to escape.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's why I walked out from the factory with the small group. and I had a friend from my hometown, from Plock, and he said, Tema, your life is at stake, so you will be nervous.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when I tell you go, and he was-- I was like in the last row of the women, he was in the first row of the men, directly behind me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, when I say go, you turn left when we all turn right.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
